<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Thank you for your visit - <%= @business.name %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #374151;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= @business_colors[:primary] %> 0%, <%= @business_colors[:secondary] %> 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .service-details {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid <%= @business_colors[:primary] %>;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: <%= @business_colors[:primary] %>;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <% if @business_logo %>
        <img src="<%= @business_logo %>" alt="<%= @business.name %>" class="logo">
      <% end %>
      <h1>Thank you, <%= @customer.first_name || @customer.name %>!</h1>
      <p>We hope you enjoyed your experience with us</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @customer.first_name || @customer.name.split.first %>,</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing <strong><%= @business.name %></strong> for your recent <%= @service.name.downcase %> experience. We hope you had a wonderful time!</p>
      
      <div class="service-details">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: <%= @business_colors[:primary] %>;">Your Experience</h3>
        <p><strong>Service:</strong> <%= @service.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @booking.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
        <% if @booking.staff_member %>
          <p><strong>Staff Member:</strong> <%= @booking.staff_member.name %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      
      <p>If you were happy with your experience, you can show your appreciation by leaving a tip for our team. Tips help support our staff and are greatly appreciated!</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @tip_url %>" class="btn">Leave a Tip</a>
      </div>
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        <em>This is a one-time secure link that expires in 7 days. Tips are optional and go directly to our team.</em>
      </p>
      
      <p>Thank you again for choosing <%= @business.name %>. We look forward to serving you again!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The <%= @business.name %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p><%= @business.name %><br>
      <% if @business.address %>
        <%= @business.address %><br>
      <% end %>
      <% if @business.phone %>
        <%= @business.phone %><br>
      <% end %>
      <%= @business.email %></p>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">
        You received this email because you recently used our services. 
        If you have any questions, please contact us directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 